        <h2>Detailed Examples to Highlight the Differences</h2>
        <p>To finalize your understanding of an <em>aupcharik aur anopcharik patra</em>, let us compare how similar situations would be handled in both formats.</p>

        <h3>Scenario: Delay in joining a destination.</h3>

        <div class="letter-box">
